    <entry>
      <title>tomcat部署插件</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/19/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/19/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="tomcat部署web项目"><a href="#tomcat部署web项目" class="headerlink" title="tomcat部署web项目"></a>tomcat部署web项目</h2><h4 id="War包"><a href="#War包" class="headerlink" title="War包"></a>War包</h4><p>War包一般是在进行Web开发时，通常是一个网站Project下的所有源码的集合，里面包含前台HTML&#x2F;CSS&#x2F;JS的代码，也包含Java的代码。</p><p>当开发人员在自己的开发机器上调试所有代码并通过后，为了交给测试人员测试和未来进行产品发布，都需要将开发人员的源码打包成War进行发布。</p><p>War包可以放在tomcat下的webapps或者word目录下，随着tomcat服务器的启动，它可以自动被解压。</p><p><strong>可以下载java源文件，用IDEA进行压缩成war</strong></p><h4 id="tomcat服务器"><a href="#tomcat服务器" class="headerlink" title="tomcat服务器"></a>tomcat服务器</h4><p>tomcat服务器是一个免费的开放源代码的Web应用服务器，属于轻量级应用服务器，在中小型系统和并发访问用户不是很多的场合下被普遍使用，是开发和调试JSP程序的首选，最新的Servlet和JSP规范总是能在tomcat中得到体现。</p><h4 id="tomcat的运行端口"><a href="#tomcat的运行端口" class="headerlink" title="tomcat的运行端口"></a>tomcat的运行端口</h4><p>tomcat默认的运行端口是8080，若想修改该端口，从根目录下进入对应的配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd conf</span><br><span class="line">vim server.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819140744079.png"></p><p>此即为运行端口，可根据需求修改为其他端口，记得打开服务器的对应端口！</p><h4 id="进入tomcat部署界面"><a href="#进入tomcat部署界面" class="headerlink" title="进入tomcat部署界面"></a>进入tomcat部署界面</h4><p>访问x.x.x.x:8080，本地部署tomcat则是localhost，服务器部署tomcat则是服务器ip</p><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819133704691.png"></p><p>点击右上角Manager App，出现403 Access Denied，原因是服务器上的tomcat没有开放远程访问的权限，此时需要修改tomcat的配置文件以开放此权限。</p><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819133821895.png"></p><h4 id="修改tomcat登录配置文件"><a href="#修改tomcat登录配置文件" class="headerlink" title="修改tomcat登录配置文件"></a>修改tomcat登录配置文件</h4><p>回到 tomcat 安装目录，进入 conf 目录，打开 tomcat-users.xml 文件，在 <tomcat-users> 标签下，添加如下配置：</tomcat-users></p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">role</span> <span class="attr">rolename</span>=<span class="string">&quot;manager-gui&quot;</span>/&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">user</span> <span class="attr">username</span>=<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span> <span class="attr">password</span>=<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span> <span class="attr">roles</span>=<span class="string">&quot;manager-gui&quot;</span>/&gt;</span>  # 用户名和密码自行设定</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启tomcat服务：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl restart tomcat (有可能要加sudo权限)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>正常情况下应该会重启服务，但是我的情况很奇怪，输出了奇怪的内容：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Failed to restart tomcat.service: Unit tomcat.service not found.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>所以我就前往bin目录下直接打开tomcat服务</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./startup.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="修改tomcat登录权限文件"><a href="#修改tomcat登录权限文件" class="headerlink" title="修改tomcat登录权限文件"></a>修改tomcat登录权限文件</h4><p>做完以上步骤后，点击右上角Manager App，发现还是403界面，说明这些配置还不够，还需要开放其他ip地址的访问权限，其实就是tomcat部署所在的服务器默认设置了本地访问的权限，我们在自己的电脑上访问需要修改远程的这个权限：</p><p>从tomcat根目录下进入manage的配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd webapps/manager/META-INF/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim context.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>原本的配置文件为：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Context</span> <span class="attr">antiResourceLocking</span>=<span class="string">&quot;false&quot;</span> <span class="attr">privileged</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">CookieProcessor</span> <span class="attr">className</span>=<span class="string">&quot;org.apache.tomcat.util.http.Rfc6265CookieProcessor&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">                   <span class="attr">sameSiteCookies</span>=<span class="string">&quot;strict&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">  &lt;-- Valve className=&quot;org.apache.catalina.valves.RemoteAddrValve&quot;</span><br><span class="line">         allow=&quot;127\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+|::1|0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Manager</span> <span class="attr">sessionAttributeValueClassNameFilter</span>=<span class="string">&quot;java\.lang\.(?:Boolean|Integer|Long|Number|String)|org\.apache\.catalina\.filters\.CsrfPreventionFilter\$LruCache(?:\$1)?|java\.util\.(?:Linked)?HashMap&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Context</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改为：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Context</span> <span class="attr">antiResourceLocking</span>=<span class="string">&quot;false&quot;</span> <span class="attr">privileged</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">CookieProcessor</span> <span class="attr">className</span>=<span class="string">&quot;org.apache.tomcat.util.http.Rfc6265CookieProcessor&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">                   <span class="attr">sameSiteCookies</span>=<span class="string">&quot;strict&quot;</span> /&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Valve className=&quot;org.apache.catalina.valves.RemoteAddrValve&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">         allow=&quot;127\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+|::1|0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1&quot; /&gt; --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Manager</span> <span class="attr">sessionAttributeValueClassNameFilter</span>=<span class="string">&quot;java\.lang\.(?:Boolean|Integer|Long|Number|String)|org\.apache\.catalina\.filters\.CsrfPreventionFilter\$LruCache(?:\$1)?|java\.util\.(?:Linked)?HashMap&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Context</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其实就是注释掉一句话，以开放其他ip的访问权限</p><h4 id="进入tomcat的manager页面："><a href="#进入tomcat的manager页面：" class="headerlink" title="进入tomcat的manager页面："></a>进入tomcat的manager页面：</h4><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819135529092.png"></p><p>找到这个部分：</p><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819135605822.png"></p><p>在下面这栏选择需要部署的文件，点击部署（需要等待一会，等待页面刷新完毕）</p><p>部署完毕后可见以下页面：</p><p><img src="/../images/tomcat%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/image-20220819140021629.png"></p><h4 id="前端引入插件："><a href="#前端引入插件：" class="headerlink" title="前端引入插件："></a>前端引入插件：</h4><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://xx.xx.xx.xx:8080/draw&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;99.8%&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1000px&quot;</span>   <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">&quot;2&quot;</span>  <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;myframe&quot;</span> <span class="attr">scrolling</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 这个draw是war包的名字，我的war包叫做draw.war，这里就是draw</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="前端访问该页面，插件显示，大功告成！"><a href="#前端访问该页面，插件显示，大功告成！" class="headerlink" title="前端访问该页面，插件显示，大功告成！"></a>前端访问该页面，插件显示，大功告成！</h4>]]></content>
      
      
      
